    <item>
      <title>诺福克南方公司将支付 6 亿美元解决俄亥俄州漏油案</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-09/norfolk-southern-to-pay-600-million-to-settle-ohio-spill-case</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法庭文件显示，诺福克南方公司表示，将支付 6 亿美元来和解针对该铁路公司的拟议集体诉讼，该诉讼涉及 2023 年俄亥俄州火车脱轨事件，该事件导致超过 100 万加仑有毒化学品泄漏并导致居民患病。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-09/norfolk-southern-to-pay-600-million-to-settle-ohio-spill-case</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Apr 2024 12:54:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>哈萨克斯坦央行寻求打破两家银行对支付的控制</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-09/kazakh-central-bank-seeks-to-break-two-lenders-grip-on-payments</link>
      <description><![CDATA[哈萨克斯坦央行希望通过明年初引入一个新系统来促进普遍准入的交易，从而削弱该国最大的两家银行对支付的控制。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-09/kazakh-central-bank-seeks-to-break-two-lenders-grip-on-payments</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Apr 2024 12:42:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
